Package studentinfo.project3

Class Student

java.lang.Object
studentinfo.project3.Student
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Student>
Direct Known Subclasses:
NonResident, Resident
public abstract class Student extends Object implements Comparable<Student>
This class contains methods that provide details of a student's first and last name, major, and credits completed.
Author:
Steven Tan, David Fabian

    • equals

      public boolean equals(Object obj)
      Compares this Student to the specified object. The result is true if the passed-in object is a Student object, the names in both profiles are the same (not case-sensitive), and the DOB are the same calendar date.
